# Django Templates

Regurlarly run `uv run djlint {FILE} --reformat` to format and `uv run djlint {FILE} --lint` to lint. Where `{FILE}` is the template you're modifying.

## Content blocks

Ensure that all endblocks are named.

BAD: `{% block content %}{% endblock %}`

GOOD: `{% block content %}{% endblock content %}`
